<div class="section section--import">
    <div class="section_content">
        <h1>$Title</h1>
        <p class="import_intro">Select a place and upload a CSV file with attraction data. Missing attractions will be created, empty fields will be filled in automatically. For differing values, you can decide which version to use in the next step.</p>

        <div class="import_uploadform">
            $UploadForm
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
